---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About Us | Herberts Travel" description="Learn about Herberts Travel - a family-run coach and bus company serving Bedfordshire, Hertfordshire and Cambridgeshire.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-navy-dark text-white py-16 sm:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold">About Us</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-white/70 text-lg max-w-2xl">A family-run business with decades of experience on the roads of Bedfordshire, Hertfordshire and Cambridgeshire.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-cream">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 sm:p-12 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-navy-dark mt-0">Our Story</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Herberts Travel has been serving the communities of Bedfordshire, Hertfordshire and Cambridgeshire for over three decades. What started as a small family operation has grown into a trusted name in local transport, providing reliable coach and bus services to schools, businesses, and community groups.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            We believe in doing things properly. Our drivers are experienced, our vehicles are meticulously maintained, and our commitment to safety is unwavering. Every journey matters to us, whether it's the daily school run or a special day trip.
          </p>

          <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-navy-dark">What Sets Us Apart</h3>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 not-prose mt-4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gold/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold-dark" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" /></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-navy-dark">Family Values</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-1">We treat every passenger like family. Personal service is what separates us from the big operators.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gold/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold-dark" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" /><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" /></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-navy-dark">Local Knowledge</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-1">We know every road, every route, and every shortcut across the counties. Experience you can trust.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gold/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold-dark" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" /></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-navy-dark">Safety Focused</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-1">Every vehicle inspected. Every driver DBS-checked. No shortcuts, no compromises.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gold/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold-dark" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-navy-dark">Reliable</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-1">When we say we'll be there, we're there. On time, every time. It's that simple.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Image Banner -->
  <section class="relative h-64 sm:h-80">
    <picture>
      <source srcset="/images/hero-bridge.webp" type="image/webp" />
      <img src="/images/hero-bridge.jpg" alt="Herberts Travel coaches crossing stone bridge at golden hour" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
    </picture>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-navy-dark/30"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-navy py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-white">Want to work with us?</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-white/70 text-lg">Whether you're a school, business, or community group — we'd love to hear from you.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center mt-8 px-8 py-3 bg-gold hover:bg-gold-dark text-white font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors text-lg">
        Get in Touch
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
